org.jmisb.api.klv.st0808

Class MessageBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0808.NaturalText
      • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0808.MessageBody
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, IAncillaryTextMetadataValue

    public class MessageBody
extends NaturalText
implements IAncillaryTextMetadataValue
    Text of the message body (ST 0808 Tag 3).

    The Ancillary Text Message Body element contains the Natural Text of the message to be encoded. This element is free text,encoded with the UTF 8-Bit Coded Character Set.

    The Ancillary Text Message Body is a mandatory element in the ancillary text metadata set.
